A South Asian snack made with potatoes (''aloo'' in Hindi/Urdu.) ''Chaat'' is a substantial snack or light meal characterized by a combination of sweet, spicy, sour and savory flavors and a mixture of textures ranging from crunchy to creamy. ''Aloo chaat'' might include spicy cooked potatoes in a cool yogurt sauce with a piquant sweet sauce and crunchy noodles on top.

